# Scamp — example environment file.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in the values
# below. The main process reads these from `process.env` at startup.
# In production / CI builds, inject the same variables via secrets
# rather than committing them.

# Sentry DSN for crash reporting.
#
# Required only when the user opts in to crash reporting at
# first launch (or via Settings → Privacy). When unset, Sentry
# silently no-ops with a console warning — the app still runs
# normally, it just doesn't transmit crashes.
#
# Get a DSN from https://sentry.io → your project →
# Settings → Client Keys (DSN).
SENTRY_DSN=
